        public void exportAnItem(boolean isIoStorage)
        Removes a StorableItem from the assigned AbstractStorage and initialises a new Package and if a Conveyor is connected, this Item is sent along it using the IndefinitePathHandler. When a AbstractIOStorage is assigned, it will first export items from its secondary processed storage.
        Parameters:
        isIoStorage - Whether the assigned building is a AbstractIOStorage.
